  "definition": {
    "en": "Freeze-dried Smallpox Vaccine Prepared in Cell Culture is a preparation for injection which is dis-solved before use. It contains live vaccinia virus."
  },
  "appearance": {
    "en": "Freeze-dried Smallpox Vaccine Prepared in Cell Culture becomes a reddish clear liquid on addition of solvent. Sodium Acetate Hydrate"
  }
